Needs Python, OpenCV 2.4.9, pip installer, MatplotLib, Numpy, FFTW3
Pip: sudo apt-get install python-pip
Numpy: sudo pip install numpy
Matplotlib: pip install matplotlib or easy_install matplotlib (in ~/)
NOTE: Matplotlib might ask for dateutil
pip install python-dateutil
NOTE: Matplotlib might ask for pyparsing
easy_install pyparsing